  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/765590/extras/228a039b7ead8bf00c2a5ba7866987bc.poster.avif?t=1524058251\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/765590/extras/228a039b7ead8bf00c2a5ba7866987bc.webm?t=1524058251\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Classic co-operative SNEK gameplay: Eat dots, get long, don't die.<br>Play together with friends both online or on the same computer.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/765590/extras/8585ec62af31d845db7c1edc014c647e.poster.avif?t=1524058251\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/765590/extras/8585ec62af31d845db7c1edc014c647e.webm?t=1524058251\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>  <strong>Co-op Levels</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">    <li>Eat dots, get long, beat the level<br>    </li><li>Play through tonnes of levels with lots of obstacles and things getting in your way. Try not to accidentally block your friends in.</li></ul>    <br>  <strong>Competitive Levels</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">    <li>Eat dots, get long, kill your friends<br>    </li><li>Go through the games levels in a random order while trying to get in the way of each other!</li></ul><br>  <strong>Endless Classic</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">    <li>Eat dots, get long... repeat<br>    </li><li>Simple empty screen with no obstacles. Get as long as you can and try to beat your previous high score.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/765590/extras/ddcbd26c5152f6f875ccb760dc7ddf9e.poster.avif?t=1524058251\" width=616 height=59 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/765590/extras/ddcbd26c5152f6f875ccb760dc7ddf9e.webm?t=1524058251\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>  <strong>Online:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">    <li>Just send your friends a game name & password to get playing!</li></ul><strong>Local:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">    <li>Full controller support for 4 players locally<br>    </li><li>Smush all your hands together on a keyboard!<br>(Note, some keyboards do not like this unless you have a \"high-end\" keyboard with n-key rollover)</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/765590/extras/c71c57297999a516abe17780eb81f836.poster.avif?t=1524058251\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/765590/extras/c71c57297999a516abe17780eb81f836.webm?t=1524058251\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>    <ul class=\"bb_ul\">        <li>Single Player: You can play by yourself, however, this game is really meant to be played with friends!<br>        </li><li>Full controller support so you can play via big picture<br>    </li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/765590/extras/988a76063d49b8469c2bdd59c4301232.poster.avif?t=1524058251\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/765590/extras/988a76063d49b8469c2bdd59c4301232.webm?t=1524058251\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>  I want to make online + local co-op games, this is my first attempt. I aimed to make a game that you could put in front of a friend & easily start having fun without lengthy explanations. I hope I have succeeded at least somewhat, please leave a review and give us much feedback as you can, it is very much appreciated!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/765590/extras/8a68259aa4d517aa4dcd4a5cf8fdbfd3.poster.avif?t=1524058251\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/765590/extras/8a68259aa4d517aa4dcd4a5cf8fdbfd3.webm?t=1524058251\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>  <ul class=\"bb_ul\">    <li>Non-music stuff: Jhomas<br>    </li><li>Trailer Music (teardrop): Amethyst Rockstars<br>    </li><li>Game Music: Eric Matyas<br>  </li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/765590/extras/228a039b7ead8bf00c2a5ba7866987bc.poster.avif?t=1524058251\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/765590/extras/228a039b7ead8bf00c2a5ba7866987bc.webm?t=1524058251\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Classic co-operative SNEK gameplay: Eat dots, get long, don't die.<br>Play together with friends both online or on the same computer.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/765590/extras/8585ec62af31d845db7c1edc014c647e.poster.avif?t=1524058251\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/765590/extras/8585ec62af31d845db7c1edc014c647e.webm?t=1524058251\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>  <strong>Co-op Levels</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">    <li>Eat dots, get long, beat the level<br>    </li><li>Play through tonnes of levels with lots of obstacles and things getting in your way. Try not to accidentally block your friends in.</li></ul>    <br>  <strong>Competitive Levels</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">    <li>Eat dots, get long, kill your friends<br>    </li><li>Go through the games levels in a random order while trying to get in the way of each other!</li></ul><br>  <strong>Endless Classic</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">    <li>Eat dots, get long... repeat<br>    </li><li>Simple empty screen with no obstacles. Get as long as you can and try to beat your previous high score.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/765590/extras/dd