ut lengthy explanations. I hope I have succeeded at least somewhat, please leave a review and give us much feedback as you can, it is very much appreciated!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/765590/extras/8a68259aa4d517aa4dcd4a5cf8fdbfd3.poster.avif?t=1524058251\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/765590/extras/8a68259aa4d517aa4dcd4a5cf8fdbfd3.webm?t=1524058251\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>  <ul class=\"bb_ul\">    <li>Non-music stuff: Jhomas<br>    </li><li>Trailer Music (teardrop): Amethyst Rockstars<br>    </li><li>Game Music: Eric Matyas<br>  </li></ul>",
